1. *Brodom* plovim Dunavom. (I sail the Danube by *ship*.)
2. Videli smo *brodove* na Savi. (We saw *ships* on the Sava.)
3. Za putovanje u Grčku odlučio sam se za *brodski* prevoz. (For the trip to Greece, I opted for *ship* transportation.)
4. Naša kompanija poseduje veliki *brodski* transporter. (Our company owns a large *ship* transporter.)
5. U luci je pristao veliki *brod*. (A large *ship* docked in the port.)
6. Ova *brodska* linija vozi do Grčke. (This *ship* line goes to Greece.)
7. Stiže nam novi *brodski* motor. (We are getting a new *ship* engine.)
8. Prijatelji su otišli na *brodski* izlet. (My friends went on a *ship* excursion.)
9. U luci su nas sačekali *brodovi*. (We were greeted by *ships* in the port.)
10. *Brodom* do ostrva. (By *ship* to the island.)